	function "id_mat" does not work for 1-by-1 matrices (sometimes; why?)
	
	* src/rte.cc: Updated (get_stepwise_transmission_matrix) to check 
	stokes_dim since id_mat did not work for 1-by-1 matrices (again; why?)

