	Convert to UTF-8.

2016-01-26  Oliver Lemke  <olemke@core-dump.info>

	* arts-2-3-422

	* src/test_propmat_partials.cc:

	Replace pow10(p) with pow(10., p). pow10 is a GNU extension and not
	available on certain operating systems / compilers.

