	version. Work in progress ...

	* src/m_rte.cc (iyEmissionStandard): Just some polishing of
	comments and indentation.

2015-12-16  Richard Larsson   <ric.larsson@gmail.com>

	* arts-2-3-392
	
	make check-all tests mostly fixed?  Memory problem...
	
