2014-11-30  Jana Mendrok  <jana.mendrok@ltu.se>

	* arts-2-3-77

	* src/m_optproperties.cc (ExtractFromMetaSingleScatSpecies):
	Don't shadow WSV with a generic one. Improved checks.

