2013-03-15  Oliver Lemke  <olemke@core-dump.info>

	* arts-2-1-551

	* src/m_doit.cc, src/methods.cc (doit_i_fieldUpdate1D):

	Remove doit_i_field_old from inputs. Instead, use a local variables
	that's initialized from doit_i_field.

