	(defocusing_sat2sat):
	* src/m_montecarlo.cc (MCGeneral):
	* src/montecarlo.cc (mcPathTraceGeneral):
	* src/m_transmitter.cc (iyRadioLink, iyTransmissionStandard):
	* src/m_rte.cc (iyEmissionStandard, iyMC):
