2012-02-24  Patrick Eriksson  <patrick.eriksson@chalmers.se>

	* arts-2-1-7

	* src/ppath.h: Changed RTOL to 1e-3, LATLONTOL to 1e-8 and POLELAT
	to 90-1e-8. These all corresponds to an overall accuracy of about 1
	mm (for Earth).

